programme.title: Bidadari: Merah Gaun Pengantin Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Almy bertemu pemuda kaya yang sombong bernama Heykal yang belajar di kolej yang sama dengannya. Almy berkawan baik dengan Faisal dan Nadia hingga terperangkap dengan cinta tiga segi. Masa sama Almy menjalin hubungan baik dengan Datin Balqis yang mengagumi bakatnya dalam bidang perunding perkahwinan. Datin Balqis menawarkan Almy menjadi perunding perkahwinan untuk anaknya, Heykal dengan Suzie. Pada mulanya Almy menolak tetapi akhinya dia berubah fikiran. Heykal menyesal dengan sikap sombongnya terhadap Almy dan akhirnya jatuh cinta. Masa yang sama Almy pula jatuh cinta dengan Faisal. Siapakah jejaka yang menjadi pilihan Almy? Pelakon: Syafiq Kyle, Nad Zainal, Fazreen Rafi, Falisha Crossley, Syed Ali, Faye Kusairi, Mimi Ernida, Alif Hadi, Nor Albaniah, Norlia Ghani, Rahim Omar, Mubarak Majid, dan Raja Ema.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Kisah 1 Rumah Ep1
programme.desc: Drama kehidupan yang mengisahkan Ika yang bekerja di sebuah caf serta Shira merupakan penyewa bilik di sebuah rumah kedai. Pada satu hari, pasangan bernama Suhaidi dan isterinya Wulan telah datang ke rumah tersebut untuk menyewa rumah mereka. Ika mengambil keputusan untuk terus tinggal di bilik sewanya dan mencari kerja di tempaty kerja Elyn, rakan serumahnya setelah tamat kolej. Namun tindakannya yang tidak memberitahu tuan rumah, telah mengundang padah! Pelakon: Nur Risteena Munir, Natasya Elyza, Abon, Raja Ema, Najwa Nasir, Kishvin, Jasmin Hamid, Hadi Tahir, Aninth Aqila, Aliff Hadi, Nur Natasya Mahyan, Zaidi Omar, Aziz M. Osman, dan Cico.

programme.desc: Mazni dan anaknya tiba di kampung tanpa pengetahuan suaminya. Mazni terkejut apabila mengetahui Aziz baru mengahwini Rahayu tanpa pengetahuannya, dia tidak dapat menerima tindakan suaminya. Mazni kecewa, dia melarikan diri balik ke bandar. Hj Abdullah menasihat Aziz supaya menerangkan kepad isterinya sebaik-baiknya. Mazni syak Halimah bersubahat dengan suaminya. Mazni balik ke kampung semula, dia menerjah Hj Abdullah semasa dia berada di rumah Mak Kiah kerana gagal memberi didikan agama kepada anak menantunya. Berlaku pergaduhan antara Aziz dengan isterinya sehingga Mazni mencabar supaya dia diceraikan. Muncul Hj Abdullah di hadapan rumah mereka, tiba-tiba dia rebah.

programme.desc: Adif meminta Sham menjaga adiknya sementara dia tiada. Afeeq memberitahu Rian tentang tawaran kerjanya sebagai Senior Manager di Port Tanjung Pelepas, dan Rian gembira untuknya. Di bilik hotel, Adif bertanya dengan siapa Rian makan, dan apabila Rian mengatakan seorang diri, Adif marah dan mendesak Rian menandatangani perjanjian hak penjagaan anak sebab ternyata Rian tidak jujur dan Adif sangka Rian ada rancangan untuk tinggalkannya. Setelah Rian menandatangani walaupun tidak setuju, Adif berubah menjadi sangat baik. Di pejabat, Adif diumumkan memiliki 20% saham syarikat. Rian di bawa jumpa dengan adik Adif iaitu Adelia, dan baru tahu Adelia di hospital mental. Rian terkejut apabila Adelia menunjukkan kebenciannya terhadap Rian.

Dia mesti menamatkan misinya dengan cepat dan satu-satunya harapan yang dia ada adalah menyakinkan Sofia untuk membantunya. Dia terjumpa sebuah bilik rahsia di dalam rumah Malik di mana tersimpan barang-barang yang jelas sekali disorok oleh Malik. Sementara itu, Sofia nampak satu pembunuhan bakal berlaku yang mengganggu perasaannya sehingga merangsang dia untuk bertindak. Dia memujuk Black untuk pulang ke kampung halaman mereka di Seri Setia untuk menyiasat kes itu. Anehnya, penyiasatan Borhan ke atas kes Nurul Najwa juga membawanya ke Seri Setia. programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep4
programme.desc: Hariz yakin Budi ada kena mengena kerana Budi ada masa dia bertengkar dengan Andy, Hariz tahu Budi adalah peminatnya, mungkin peminat ini bunuh mereka yang cuba sakiti Hariz.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep5
programme.desc: Hariz terpaksa dibebaskan semula, dan saat inilah Hariz mahu larikan dirinya, dia kembali ke kabin yang mana dia lihat sudah berubah kedudukan, dia yakin pembunuh masih ada di situ. Banyak rahsia disimpan sang penulis novel ini kian dirungkai.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep6
programme.desc: Haridz dikunjungi seorang lelaki misteri. Ganesh tidak tahu tentang kejadian ini, dia sendiri fikir kes ini sudah habis, namun kemudiannya mayat Pokwe ditemui di kawasan kampung.

programme.title: Hilang Kasyorga EP4 Ep4
programme.desc: Rodi menyelamatkan beberapa kanak-kanak dari sindiket pemerdagangan manusia tetapi gagal menemui Kasyorga. Kak Esah panik apabila mendapati Reza menyembunyikan kanak-kanak di rumahnya dan memaksanya keluar. Datuk Zaza arahkan Reza bunuh kanak-kanak dan Esah, tapi Reza hanya menurut separuh. Rodi menculik Datuk Zaza, bertukar tebusan dengan Reza namun budak itu bukan Kasyorga. Rodi bunuh mereka berdua. Sara curiga dengan Madam Kwan dan Uncle Lim. Akhirnya, rahsia terbongkar:

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: A hero cop accidentally leads his team into a trap from which he is the only survivor. Drowning his guilt in booze, he is eventually assigned a new younger partner who turns out to have his own secrets.

programme.title: School Tales
programme.desc: Ahli-ahli pancaragam membina hubungan erat semasa kem tahunan mereka dan memutuskan untuk mencabar nasib dengan "menguji" legenda hantu yang menyelubungi sekolah mereka.

programme.title: Fly By Night
programme.desc: Seorang pemandu teksi menggunakan perkhidmatannya sebagai penyamaran untuk kegiatan pemerasan, dan apabila tingkah laku adiknya yang impulsif menarik perhatian polis dan kumpulan samseng ke ambang pintu mereka, dia sanggup melakukan apa sahaja demi melindungi orang-orang yang penting dalam hidupnya.

programme.title: Pintu Neraka
programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan tentang Kamasani, seorang tokoh perniagaan yang menghidap kanser tahap akhir, yang mencari Mahabub, seorang pertapa misteri yang dikhabarkan memiliki penawar. Selepas menjalani rawatan yang mahal, Kamasani merasakan penyakitnya semakin berkurang, namun dia mula mengalami kesan sampingan yang serius; dia berhalusinasi dan menjadi ganas. Titik perubahan berlaku apabila Vida, seorang wartawan televisyen, membongkar konspirasi ghaib Mahabub yang melibatkan nama-nama besar. Kamasani akhirnya sedar bahawa ramai yang telah menderita atau mati akibat keengganannya menerima takdir sendiri, lalu bertekad untuk membetulkan segalanya.

programme.title: SAM
programme.desc: Sam, yang pernah menjalinkan hubungan intim dengan rakan sekerjanya, mendapati bahawa bukan dirinya sahaja yang menyukai Lisa. Suatu hari, Lisa telah diculik dan Sam bertekad untuk menyelamatkan Lisa serta mencari dalang di sebalik penculikan itu tanpa menyedari bahawa perkara itu akan mengubah hidupnya selama-lamanya.

programme.title: Mat Moto
programme.desc: Filem ini mengikuti perjalanan sekumpulan "mat moto", iaitu penunggang motosikal yang berkongsi minat yang sama dalam sukan permotoran. Dalam pengembaraan merentasi Malaysia, mereka menemui erti sebenar persahabatan dan kegembiraan berkongsi hobi yang sama.

programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift 2
programme.desc: Zack dan Sham adalah dua nama yang sinonim dengan istilah keakraban. Hubungan sebagai dua sahabat karib yang sama-sama berkongsi hobi dan minat dalam bidang perlumbaan kereta 'drift'.

programme.title: Fly By Night
programme.desc: Seorang pemandu teksi menggunakan perkhidmatannya sebagai penyamaran untuk kegiatan pemerasan, dan apabila tingkah laku adiknya yang impulsif menarik perhatian polis dan kumpulan samseng ke ambang pintu mereka, dia sanggup melakukan apa sahaja demi melindungi orang-orang yang penting dalam hidupnya.

programme.title: Budak Pendamping
programme.desc: Ia mengisahkan tentang seorang budak yang berumur 16 tahun, bernama Firash. Dibesarkan sebagai seorang anak tunggal di sebuah keluarga yang sentiasa sibuk dengan kerjaya, membuatkan Firash lebih senang bersendiriaan. Disebabkan itu keluarganya membuat keputusan untuk hantarnya ke sebuah kem. Disana Firash bertembung dengan Idlan dan rakannya Khai dan Sahar, serta sebahagian dalam Ahli Majlis Tertinggi Asrama (AMTA) bagi kem tersebut. Akibat ketidakpuasan mereka terhadap Firash yang kelihatan lembik, badannya menjadi tempat untuk mereka lepaskan kekerasan. Namun kehadiran budak pendamping mengubah segalanya untuk Firash tetapi ia juga menggugat kesejahteraan yang dah lama tidak bergelora. Lantas, adakah perjanjian antara Firash dan pendampingnya merupakan ilusi semata - mata ataupun terdapat hutang yang akan dituntut antaranya dengan Tuan Daud?

programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep3
programme.desc: Di tengah-tengah suasana yang tidak menentu, Melati dan Golok dikejutkan dengan kedatangan tetamu luar biasa, Wewe Gombel, yang telah menghidu mangsanya di halaman Melati Inn. Ketika Melati dan Golok cuba mengejar dan menundukkannya, rahsia silam Melati terbongkar, akhirnya membawa Wewe Gombel untuk mencari apa yang dia cari.

programme.title: Battle of the Fist
programme.desc: Khoa berpindah ke sekolah baru, di mana dia menyertai kelab Vo Ta dan jatuh hati kepada Khanh Trang, gadis cantik yang mahir dalam seni mempertahankan diri dan mempunyai ramai peminat. Ketika dia mengikut kata hatinya, masalah seolah-olah sentiasa menemuinya di mana sahaja dia berada.

programme.title: SAM
programme.desc: Sam, yang pernah menjalinkan hubungan intim dengan rakan sekerjanya, mendapati bahawa bukan dirinya sahaja yang menyukai Lisa. Suatu hari, Lisa telah diculik dan Sam bertekad untuk menyelamatkan Lisa serta mencari dalang di sebalik penculikan itu tanpa menyedari bahawa perkara itu akan mengubah hidupnya selama-lamanya.

programme.title: Motif
programme.desc: Seorang penyiasat polis yang tegas terlibat dalam kes orang hilang di luar kawasan, sementara dia sendiri bergelut untuk menyesuaikan diri dengan peranannya sebagai isteri kedua dalam sebuah perkahwinan poligami.

programme.title: Sayang
programme.desc: Pelajar kolej swasta, Noni sering dikawal ketat oleh abangnya, Herman dan tidak boleh keluar bersosial seperti temannya yang lain. Herman mula bertindak menjadi ketua keluarga setelah kematian bapa mereka setahun yang lalu. Noni menghadiri satu majlis hari jadi dan terjadi sesuatu yang membuatkan Herman semakin ketat mengawal gerak geri Noni.

programme.title: Reaksiar Ep2
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Nada Siar Ep46
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Ruang Temu Ep46
programme.desc: Program temu bual bersama Nam Ron yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi beliau berkaitan pengalaman beliau di dalam industri seni

programme.title: Sayang Salmah
programme.desc: Semangat cinta akan bangsa dan negara diterapkan dalam diri Hassan dan Salleh selaku anak kepada Encik Jabar dan Dasimah yang inginkan anak mereka mempunyai rasa patriotik akan negara. Hassan, aktif dalam bidang politik manakala Salleh menjadi seorang pemuda liar yang suka berhibur. Segalanya berubah apabila ayah mereka meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Teruna Idaman
programme.desc: Leha, seorang gadis lincah dan berdikari, sering menolak pinangan yang diatur ibunya. Alasannya mudah dia belum bersedia dan belum bertemu jejaka idaman. Setiap kali ada rombongan merisik, Leha rela berpura-pura kurang siuman semata-mata mahu menggagalkan rancangan perkahwinan itu. Namun, segalanya berubah apabila Tengku Iskandar, seorang pegawai baharu yang kacak dan berkarisma, muncul di tempat kerjanya. Buat pertama kali, hati Leha mula terusik. Demi menarik perhatian Iskandar, Leha sanggup lakukan apa saja termasuk mengorbankan wang simpanannya. Tapi adakah cinta berbalas, atau sekadar angan-angan?

programme.title: Reaksiar Ep2
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Nada Siar Ep46
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Ruang Temu Ep46
programme.desc: Program temu bual bersama Nam Ron yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi beliau berkaitan pengalaman beliau di dalam industri seni

programme.title: Penghujung Jalan
programme.desc: Mastura, seorang wanita muda yang terlanjur cinta, terpaksa menanggung akibat apabila hamil luar nikah. Selepas melahirkan, dia nekad meninggalkan bayinya di hadapan rumah Aina dan Rosli, pasangan suami isteri yang masih meratapi kehilangan anak akibat keguguran. Kehadiran bayi itu seolah-olah menghidupkan semula harapan mereka untuk menjadi ibu bapa. Namun, apabila pihak berkuasa campur tangan demi siasatan, bayi itu terpaksa diambil semula. Hal ini meninggalkan Aina dalam kesedihan yang mendalam, sekali lagi kehilangan sesuatu yang sangat berharga.

programme.title: Merah
programme.desc: Pilihan antara baik atau buruk menentukan di mana pengakhiran jalan kisah hidup Merah. Terpaksa menjalani hukuman penjara akibat pilihan yang dibuatnya, Merah bertemu seseorang yang istimewa. Kasih, seorang kaunselor menemui Merah. Namun, ada rahsia yang disimpan erat oleh Kasih. Meskipun menyukai antara satu sama lain, pelbagai halangan terpaksa mereka tempuhi bersama.

programme.title: Namaku Yassin
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Yanto, seorang penjual jagung bakar yang menjalani kehidupan sederhana di kampung. Segalanya berubah apabila dia bertemu semula dengan sahabat lamanya, Budi, yang baru pulang setelah beberapa tahun bekerja di Malaysia. Terkesima dengan kejayaan Budi, Yanto menerima pelawaan untuk turut sama mengubah nasibnya di Kuala Lumpur. Menggunakan nama samaran "Yassin", dia bekerja sebagai buruh di tapak pembinaan dan bersahabat dengan Mahmud. Di sebalik cabaran hidup di kota, Yassin turut menemui cinta dalam diri Liza, seorang pengurus di tempat kerjanya. Namun, perjalanan mencari rezeki dan erti kehidupan ini tidak semudah yang disangka.

programme.title: Gadis Hitam Putih
programme.desc: Kota Jakarta telah digemparkan dengan berita kejadian lebih 20 tahun lalu. Dalam satu perbicaraan di mahkamah, seorang jururawat bernama Mira mengaku telah menukar bayi dua keluarga yang mempunyai latar belakang yang berbeza. Mira bertindak sebegitu kerana dia ingin membalas dendam terhadap seorang doktor yang memutuskan cintanya kerana perbezaan darjat keturunan.

programme.title: Ilhamku
programme.desc: Sham, seorang lelaki weirdo yang kreatif dan gemar menghadapi cabaran, bersetuju menjadi juri bagi sebuah uji bakat atas permintaan sahabatnya, Shima. Di situlah dia bertemu dengan Noreen, seorang penyanyi baharu yang berbakat namun bermasalah. Meskipun Noreen sering menimbulkan pelbagai masalah di syarikat rakaman kerana sikap tidak berdisiplinnya, Sham yang jatuh hati padanya sentiasa memaafkan segala kesilapannya. Namun, kasih sayang tanpa batas itu akhirnya memakan diri apabila Noreen semakin angkuh dan mula mempergunakan Sham demi kepentingan peribadinya.

programme.title: Sayang
programme.desc: Pelajar kolej swasta, Noni sering dikawal ketat oleh abangnya, Herman dan tidak boleh keluar bersosial seperti temannya yang lain. Demi mempertahankan keselamatan, pihak British berusaha menubuhkan pasukan Home Guard. Namun, dalam kekalutan yang melanda, muncul beberapa pengkhianat yang menjadi tali barut komunis, lantas mencetuskan kekacauan dan ketegangan yang kian meruncing dalam komuniti kampung itu.

Demi menarik perhatian Iskandar, Leha sanggup lakukan apa saja termasuk mengorbankan wang simpanannya. Tapi adakah cinta berbalas, atau sekadar angan-angan?

Pada masa tersebut, Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar baru dua tahun berkahwin. programme.title: Sampai 7 Keturunan
programme.desc: Dalam satu peraduan cabutan bertuah, Aidil telah terpilih untuk memenangi percutian lima hari empat malam di sebuah hotel lima bintang serta wang tunai sebanyak lima ribu ringgit. Namun begitu, disebabkan isterinya Syikin yang sedang hamil, Aidil memutuskan untuk tidak mengambil percutian tersebut. Walaupun begitu, Aidil berasa sayang untuk melepaskan hadiah itu begitu sahaja. Setelah dipujuk berkali-kali, Pak Karim akhirnya bersetuju walaupun masih risaukan ayamnya.

programme.title: Aji Noh Motor
programme.desc: Aji ialah seorang abang yang sangat mengambil berat dan sanggup melakukan apa sahaja untuk adiknya, Noh. Noh, seorang yang berpegang kepada ajaran Islam, berasa tidak senang dengan tabiat Aji yang suka berlumba haram. Noh dilahirkan buta dan menjalani kehidupannya dengan melakukan perkara-perkara yang berfaedah, manakala abangnya pula gemar menyertai perlumbaan haram dan melepak bersama rakan-rakannya. Walaupun Aji mempunyai perangai yang tidak baik, dia sangat menyayangi Noh. Dia sanggup memenuhi permintaan Noh walaupun permintaan itu mustahil untuk dicapai. Semuanya bermula pada hari lahir Noh apabila dia menyatakan hasrat untuk menunaikan haji. Aji yang tidak mampu untuk menunaikan permintaan tersebut telah berusaha mengumpul wang demi merealisasikan impian adiknya. Walaupun terpaksa melakukan perkara yang haram dan bertentangan dengan agama.

programme.title: Peluang Ketiga
programme.desc: Zulaikha dan Yusuf telah menjalinkan hubungan sejak zaman universiti lagi. Namun, hubungan mereka terputus apabila Yusuf tidak bersetuju dengan keputusan Zulaikha untuk menjadi seorang penyanyi. Zulaikha kemudian bertemu dengan Mikhail, seorang lelaki berhati mulia yang sentiasa menyokong segala impiannya. Sementara itu, Yusuf meneruskan kerjayanya sebagai pelumba basikal profesional dan jatuh cinta dengan seorang wartawan sukan bernama Alya.Namun, apabila Mikhail melamar Zulaikha, hati Yusuf mula dilanda cemburu. Mampukah Yusuf melupakan Zulaikha dan menerima hakikat bahawa cinta mereka mungkin sudah berlalu?

programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Tetapi apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik dimasukkan ke penjara, lebih banyak kekacauan berlaku dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh berbeza daripada realiti.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 3
programme.desc: NADIA dan WAWA disahkan mengandung! ADNAN gembira kerana akhirnya dia bakal menjadi seorang bapa. Dia bersedia untuk menjaga NADIA, tetapi sebaliknya, dia yang mengalami alahan pagi dan pelbagai gejala kehamilan. Sementara itu, WAWA dan BOBBY menjalani kehidupan yang sederhana dan menghadapi masalah kewangan. WAWA mula marah kepada BOBBY kerana mereka tidak mempunyai cukup wang semasa tempoh kehamilannya dan menjelang kelahiran. Sebagai seorang kawan yang baik, ADNAN meminjamkan wang kepada BOBBY. Namun, BOBBY tidak lagi berani meminta wang daripada ADNAN selepas dimarahi olehnya yang tertekan dengan keadaan NADIA. Akibat desakan hidup, BOBBY membuat keputusan untuk berlumba semula.

programme.title: Sampai 7 Keturunan
programme.desc: Dalam satu peraduan cabutan bertuah, Aidil telah terpilih untuk memenangi percutian lima hari empat malam di sebuah hotel lima bintang serta wang tunai sebanyak lima ribu ringgit. Namun begitu, disebabkan isterinya Syikin yang sedang hamil, Aidil memutuskan untuk tidak mengambil percutian tersebut. Walaupun begitu, Aidil berasa sayang untuk melepaskan hadiah itu begitu sahaja. Dia memberikan wang tunai dan tiket tersebut kepada Pak Karim, yang pada mulanya keberatan untuk menerimanya kerana bimbang meninggalkan ayam kesayangannya. programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: Love Lies
programme.desc: Gynaecologist Veronica downloads a dating app for fun. Little does she know that the charming French engineer on the other end is actually a local con artist named Joe, who is a member of an online scam group. As their fake relationship unfolds, both Joes guilty conscience and Veronicas hopes intensify.

programme.title: Endless Battle
programme.desc: This is a story about two brothers. The younger brother is a drug lord while the elder brother Zhong is a police officer in the Narcotics Bureau. Both are involved in a drug cartels turf battle and during an escort mission, Zhong discovers his brothers hidden identity. This leads to an endless battle between good and evil.

programme.title: The Way We Are
programme.desc: Set in Tin Shui Wai, a marginalised satellite town, Kwai is a middle-aged widow who works hard in a neighbourhood supermarket to support herself and her son. They lead a mundane but fulfilling life. When an elderly woman who lives alone moved in to Tin Shui Wai, Kwai strikes up a friendship with her and helps her ease into a new life.

programme.title: Fatal Visit
programme.desc: Yanny leaves Hong Kong for San Jose to visit her old friend Ling. Ling and her husband Tang seems to live an ideal and carefree life. However, during her five-day stay, Yanny uncovers the truth behind the faade as she reveals the unspeakable secrets that will propel all three down a fatal path of destruction.

programme.title: Old Fox
programme.desc: In 1989, young Liao Jie and his father save for a home, unaware of rising property prices. Frustrated by poverty, he learns from their landlord Old Fox who teaches him survival in society. Liao Jie ends up hurting Old Fox with what he has learnt, but his empathy prevents him from becoming like Old Fox.

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: Another Me
programme.desc: Constable Li Mao marries a rich girl but her parents disapprove of their marriage. One day, Li accidentally discovers that he looks exactly like the prince! While he aims to secure a high ranking position in the palace, the prince wants freedom, so they decide to switch identities. This however, got them both involved in the ministers conspiracy

programme.title: The Sparring Partner
programme.desc: Adapted from a sensational 2013 parricide in Hong Kong, a young man partners with his friend to murder and dismember his parents. Pleading not guilty, the defendants play the devil and idiot game, while the defense attorneys turn on each other. Meanwhile, heated debates emerge inside the jury room, where nine jurors grapple with the truth.

programme.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from real events. Detective Lin sets up a special unit to arrest the motorbike robber and the crime syndicate behind the thefts in Foshan. In the process, his pregnant wife is hit by a motorbike robber, leading him to uncover their revenge plan...

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: Crisis Negotiators
programme.desc: Negotiator Wai becomes the prime suspect in a police murder case. He takes hostages at the police station and demands to negotiate with former negotiator Jun. As the two engage in a high-stake battle of wits, their expertise in psychological manipulation leads to a tense verbal sparring match, gradually shifting their positions and mind sets.

programme.title: Hong Kong Family
programme.desc: Eight years ago, the family in a Hakka-walled village was torn apart during a combative winter solstice dinner. Eight years later, their cousin returns home from England and seeks to reunite the family for another winter solstice dinner. While things seem to be falling apart, this dinner may well be an opportunity to mend relations.

programme.title: My Kung Fu Sweetheart
programme.desc: Phoenixs (Cecilia Cheung) parents are martial arts superheroes, who hide their true identities while ferreting out evil martial artists. Phoenix gets the go-ahead to train in the misty mountains, where she learns of her all-important romantic destiny...

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: The Locksmith
programme.desc: Locksmith Master Shan suffers from dementia and passes on his skills to Hao Ren, who surpasses him. Detective Liu often seeks Hao Ren's help and they become good friends. When Hao Ren reunites with an old friend one day, he accidentally unfolds the truth behind Shan's wife's disappearance, leading to a chain of mysterious events.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Love Punch
programme.desc: Talented boxer Jia Yang is caught in an underground fight to clear her father's debts. She loses her Olympic aspiration and vanishes from the boxing world. 10 years later, Coach Li Yue is determined to help her honour her father's wish by returning to the ring. As passion and obligation collide, can Jia Yang revive her abandoned boxing dream?

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koos real identity?

programme.title: Someday or One Day
programme.desc: The movie is a spin-off from the TV series of the same name. While Huang Yu Xuan mourns the death of her boyfriend, she receives a mysterious cassette player that allows her to travel back in time. She meets her boyfriend then again, but will she be able to change his destiny?

programme.title: VR Fighter
programme.desc: Bodyguard Long Wei has posttraumatic stress disorder after his wife's death. One day, he encounters Amy who works for a VR technology firm and is invited for a new product test. After the test, Long Wei becomes the firms VR fighter and dons the newly invented armour. However, as mysterious armed men break in, a fierce battle has just begun...

programme.title: The Goldfinger
programme.desc: Inspired by Hong Kongs biggest financial scandal in the 1980s, this is a rags to riches story about Ching Yat Yin who is chairman of a listed company. With Chings wealth and influence on the rise, ICAC senior investigator Lau Kai Yuen is determined to investigate the case, even if it means spending 15 years in pursuit of the truth.

programme.title: Wish Comes True
programme.desc: Xiao Fei is a cheerful girl who has been abandoned by her mother. One day, she encounters a gifted young man named Zi Wai, who is battling a rare disease. Determined to help him, she embarks on a journey to find his lost love. Even when they discover that the drug treating Wai is ineffective, they choose to embrace hope and love together.

programme.title: Mission Milano
programme.desc: A wealthy entrepreneur goes undercover with an Interpol agent to protect a new invention, the Seed of God, from falling into an international crime conglomerate.

programme.title: YUM Investigation
programme.desc: YUM is a detective agency that handles supernatural cases. As YUM investigates the evil spirits appearing in an old building, they discover that the spirits are created by a spirit master to haunt the residents so that the building can be vacated for redevelopment. Can the YUM investigators finally find ways to fight against the master?

programme.title: Romantic Dream
programme.desc: Dino meets his dream girl Mandy and falls in love with her at first sight. However, she disappears suddenly and he only sees her again after nine years, when she is already married. To overcome the pain of losing his love, Dino finds a guru with supernatural power to make him meet Mandy in his dream.

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard, who suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Young Ip Man: Crisis Time
programme.desc: Set in 1917, young Ip Man pursues his studies in Hong Kong. The school is held hostage on the day of an English speech competition, and as Ip Man decides to step up and fight the crisis, it is revealed that his master and his childhood friend are behind all this. Can he take them down and uphold justice?

programme.title: Apartment for Ladies
programme.desc: A Taiwanese singer comes to Hong Kong in search for her missing younger sister, who had arrived in Hong Kong to be discovered as a nightclub singer. She finds lodging at an apartment for women run by a man-hating landlady, Mrs Chan. However, Mrs Chan cannot confine the young ladies youthful vitality within the apartment.

programme.title: The Black Enforcer
programme.desc: Lung the Black Enforcer is ordered to escort a murderer Fei to prison. While taking shelter in Lungs house from the snowstorm, Fei is rescued by his gang and Fei kills Lungs mother and sister before escaping. Lung is imprisoned for the failed task and after being released, he vows to avenge his family by killing Fei.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jins daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: One Way Only
programme.desc: Danny is a motorbike workshop owner, once was a renowned motorcycle racer, but were seriously injured in an illegal race. Mai, student of Danny, wins a race in Macau under Danny's help. However, because of money and honour, Mai joins illegal races. After knowing this, Li persuades Mai to stop illegal races, but Mai seems cannot find his way out

programme.title: The Land of Many Perfumes
programme.desc: Monk Tang San Zang, Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing find themselves in Womanland, where women only give birth to baby girls and do so by drinking the magical spring water.

programme.title: The Iron Buddha
programme.desc: After a notorious rapist Xiao kills his master and the entire clan, Han the last surviving disciple, decides to take revenge. He must find the legendary Hulong Blade to counter Xiao's Evil Poisonous Sword, but as Han has never seen Xiao before, he is deceived when Xiao poses as an ally to try and steal his Blade in the process.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Tea House
programme.desc: Big Brother Cheng fled from the mainland to Hong Kong, where he opened a teahouse in a housing estate, hoping to find a peaceful life. However, relentless provocations from local triad gangs go unaddressed by the police, prompting Cheng and his friends at the teahouse to seek revenge.

programme.title: Illicit Desire
programme.desc: This instant cult classic adapts three erotic and mystical tales from the Chinese classical works, with stories spanning across time from the Tang to Ming dynasties. The stories, filled with characters such as emperors, concubines, monks and fortune-tellers, intertwine in a world of adultery, lust and greed, alongside great costumes!

programme.title: King Eagle
programme.desc: A young swordman, King Eagle, unwillingly gets involved in the internal affairs of a powerful clan and becomes their target. He is saved by the female chief of the clan, Lin, and falls in love with her. However, Lins sister is part of all evil plots and betrays her. Even so, Lin begs King Eagle not to harm her sister.

programme.title: Reincarnated Swordsman
programme.desc: A Wu Dang disciple Fu, kills the chief of Wu Dang Clan and frames it on the chiefs illegitimate child, Yun. Fu then proclaims himself the new chief and orders the killing of Yun, who vows to avenge his fathers death and learns the invincible silkworm martial arts style in order to defeat Fu.

programme.title: Tales of Larceny
programme.desc: Connecting all the antics of bosses, monks, beggars, and thieves is the slippery and sinuous efforts of three pickpockets so adept at their chosen skill that they can even trick three beauties of their underwear without missing a step.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: Huan Zhu's ghost seeks help from Fake Ghost Catchers Bao Tuo and Zhou Peng, after a jealous suitor's ghost seeks vengeance by murdering her and now targeting her sister. Together with actor Wu Shun Chao who possesses a supernatural talent, they unite to protect Huan Zhu's sister from both mortal and spectral threats.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: That Fiery Girl
programme.desc: The bandits of Hulu Valley slay the chief of the Mei Clan while searching for a treasure map. In retaliation, Chun from the Mei Clan infiltrates the bandit's fortress to map a way in for the authorities, but ends up falling in love with the bandit leader's daughter, Pearl. While Chuns plot is uncovered, he receives unexpected help from Pearl.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: Vengeance
programme.desc: Yu Lou is betrayed by his wife and eventually killed by her lover, Fung, who is the boss of a martial arts school. Yu Lous brother, Xiao Lou, knows about his tragic death and is determined to take revenge for him.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: The Twelve Gold Medallions
programme.desc: This was one of top three films of 1970 and winner of "Outstanding Drama" at the 9th Golden Horse Awards. The evil minister uses twelve golden medallions to summon war hero Yueh Fei back from the frontline and execute him. A group of wandering warriors, led by Yueh Hua and Chin Ping, try to stop the medallion couriers.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Five Shaolin Masters
programme.desc: The Qing court plots to kill all Shaolin disciples by burning down Shaolin Temple. This sudden fire killed almost everyone except for five disciples. To take revenge on the Qing court, the five of them train hard in different fighting styles to become The Five Shaolin Masters.

programme.title: The Voyage of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung continues his incognito voyage to southern China. Accompanied by the minister and the imperial scholar, they have many amusing encounters in Yangzhou.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre 2
programme.desc: Only by bringing together the powerful Heaven Sword and the mighty Dragon Sabre can six martial arts sects struggling for supremacy be saved in this thrilling sequel to Chu Yuan's original hit.

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: Return Of The Dead
programme.desc: A long-awaited horror sequel after Enchanted Shadow, this is about three asylum inmates telling their stories. In story one, a husband and wife discover they should be careful what they wish for. A naked female ghost seeks revenge from her watery grave in story two, and a dead prostitute returns as a ghost in the last tale.

programme.title: Vengeance is a Golden Blade
programme.desc: Convoy Master Lis wife has an affair with his rival Long, who plans to steal Lis Golden Blade and kill him as well as his young daughter. Li and his daughter manage to escape and the latter grows up to be a skilled swordswoman who vows to avenge her mothers death a lie told by Li. The truth is revealed when she sees her mother alive by chance.

programme.title: The Shadow Boxing
programme.desc: Chan and his apprentice Fan transport vampires for a living. In their most recent job, they are hired to transport nine zombies at one go. When two of them hopped away, it is revealed that one of them is actually a man in disguise trying to escape from his enemies. It turns out that the fake zombie and Chan are both martial arts experts!

programme.title: The Enchantress
programme.desc: Shot on the Shaws' lot in the final years of Hong Kong's greatest studio, The Enchantress tells the story of martial artists who disappear in the night! Intrigued, wanna-be detective/swordsman Feng Chi-wu (Mok Siu-chung) is determined to find out what is happening. But when Feng finds out that an evil vampire spirit (Wei Chiu-hua) is killing swordsmen, he's in for more than he bargains for... It's an outlandish fairy-tale and martial arts fantasy, where your fists and sword aren't nearly enough!

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Super Inframan
programme.desc: Transformed from a young laboratory researcher, the thunderbolt-fisted Inframan must battle Princess Dragon Mom who wakes up from hibernation to conquer the earth with her army of mutant monsters.

programme.title: Fangs of the Cobra
programme.desc: Incredibly, the title serpent is not a harbinger of horror, but actually the film's hero. This virtuous viper sniffs out bombs, fights gangs, battles a baby-killing rodent and even takes on a duplicitous woman. This one-of-a-kind thriller will be applauded by reptile fans everywhere.

programme.title: Call to Arms
programme.desc: The aggressive and dangerous Chin Empire conquers the hard-put Chao kingdom while the Wei empire is drained of its heroes and paralyzed by an indecisive ruler. Adventure, intrigue, death and tragedy reigns before the triumphant clash of the armies.

programme.title: The 5 Billion Dollar Legacy
programme.desc: A crippled billionaire mails a letter to each of his long-lost daughters inviting them to go to Japan, in the hope that he will find a worthy heir to inherit his vast fortune. The sisters finally meet abroad the plane to Japan, and one of them is taken with a man who is going to investigate the death of his lawyer uncle in a mysterious hit-and-run.

programme.title: Mission Impossible
programme.desc: A sword masters daughter is pursued and poisoned by an evil master when bringing back the stolen Golden Sword to the palace. She dies on the run and returns as a spirit to take revenge by killing the evil master, and soon vanishes after returning the sword to the emperor.

programme.title: Moonlight Serenade
programme.desc: A sweet inn-keepers daughter is witness to a perverted rape, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle. Can her true love rescue her in time? For this movie, the moonlight serenade is the sound of suspense, leading to more danger than most romantic dramas can handle.

programme.title: Tanu Weds Manu
programme.desc: Manu, an NRI doctor, comes to India in search of a bride and falls in love with Tanu.

programme.title: Sangathamizhan
programme.desc: A young man falls for the daughter of an industrialist with a dark past.

programme.title: Anwar
programme.desc: A Muslim man in love with a Hindu woman is mistaken for a terrorist.

programme.title: Ishqiya
programme.desc: Two rogues on the run and a pretty widow elaborately plan to kidnap an industrialist.

programme.title: Devdas
programme.desc: Prohibited to marry the love of his life, Devdas seeks the path of self-destruction.

programme.title: Hum Tumhare hai Sanam
programme.desc: Gopal and Radha's marriage turns sour when Radha gets overly concerned with Suraj's work.

programme.title: Dil
programme.desc: A man's plan backfires after he pretends to be rich in order to get his son married.

programme.title: Om Shanti Om
programme.desc: A junior artist falls in love with an actress only to die and be reborn as a superstar.

programme.title: Devdas

programme.desc: A cyclist in Mumbai is destined to rediscover his family legacy of fighting injustice.

programme.title: Baaz: A Bird in Danger
programme.desc: A woman who is in love with a murder suspect helps the police track down a serial killer.

programme.title: Dedh Bigha Zameen
programme.desc: A man fights political obstacles to sell his land and get his sister married.

programme.title: Bhediya
programme.desc: Bhaskar is attacked by a wolf and soon starts to transform into a shape-shifter.

programme.title: Deewane Huye Paagal
programme.desc: Karan follows his ladylove to Dubai only to realise that she is pursued by other suitors.

programme.title: Rangeela
programme.desc: Both Munna and Raj Kamal love Mili, who nurtures the dream of becoming a big star.

programme.title: Amar Akbar Anthony
programme.desc: Three brothers set out to take revenge on those responsible for their separation.

programme.desc: The CEO of an advertising agency is accused of sexually harassing his protege.

programme.title: Gandhi
programme.desc: Mohandas Gandhi urges non-violent resistance to liberate India from British colonialism.

programme.title: Nastik
programme.desc: Shankar becomes an atheist and vows revenge on Tiger, the man who killed his father.

programme.title: Golmaal 3
programme.desc: Two sets of adult siblings turn hostile when their respective single parents get married.

programme.desc: Video game adventurer Lara Croft comes to life in a movie where she races against time and villains to recover powerful ancient artifacts.

programme.desc: Lara Croft (Jolie) is back in action and faces her most perilous mission: to recover what ancient civilization believed to be the essence of all evil, Pandora's Box.

programme.desc: A stranger in San Miguel becomes involved in a vendetta between two families. Playing one family against the other, he rescues a beautiful woman from captivity.

programme.title: The Lovely Bones
programme.desc: When 14-year-old Susie Salmon was murdered, she left her unfinished life behind. But now from her place in a strange but beautiful in-between world, she must help her father catch her killer and protect her family before she can finally move on. Filled with thrilling suspense, hope and the redeeming power of love.

programme.title: Confidence
programme.desc: Jake Vig is a con man with a gift for duplicity and a natural charm. Now hes cooked up the con of a lifetime to even the score for the murder of a buddy, pay back those he owes, and get the hell out of the business while hes still drawing breath.

programme.desc: When a clerical error causes a clash in wedding dates, two best friends who'd do anything for each other find themselves in a no-holds-barred, take-no-prisoners struggle that threatens to erupt into all-out war.

programme.desc: World's Dumbest Thrillseekers 11 - Feel the endorphin rush as 20 of the World's Dumbest Thrillseekers do their thing.

programme.desc: Cool - Clark has a chance to share a night out on the town with Lana, thanks to Lex's matchmaking, but the evening is interrupted when Clark faces an icy enemy, Sean Kelvin (MICHAEL CORISTINE).

And why are they all back in spring?

programme.title: SHErlock Ep1
programme.desc: It is the first all-female immersive reasoning program. Six guests form a female reasoning team and immerse themselves in workplace life. The program uses single-episode puzzles and long-term plots to advance in two dimensions, gradually unlocking and reasoning the truth. Through each episode of popularizing legal issues, the causes of the case and the social hot spots behind it are analyzed, and the legal principles and emotions around us are felt.
